name: Vedain
Lore: 'Kajain''sa''Nikto scout. Sold by his family into slavery to Jabba. Gambler. Plays sabacc with his fellow Nikto.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Tatooine. During your control phase, if at a Jabba''s Palace site, may use 2 Force to make a ''wager''. Both players draw one destiny. Player with lower number loses 1 Force.',
